Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4月份 昂魔法学院迎接着新生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问询处在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领了学生卡的同学请去体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈是这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和五十岛被委托在入学式帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是如出一辙呢 这里和我们生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我家的妹妹也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是编入初等部的伊田二叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊田的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:15.20,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1047,642)\blur1\fad(450,450)}巫师气息的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是一三的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是七濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这个可怕的阿姨是五十岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是阿姨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吐槽可怕这个词没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来承蒙你们关照我家的一三了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是承蒙关照 我是七濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是受了不少关照呢 我叫五十岛胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是伊田一三的妹妹 二叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道其实没有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者只有伊田是从桥下捡来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是如假包换的我的妹妹啊 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:03:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱也没办法啊 谁让她是我抚养大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是世界第一可爱 宇宙第一的好女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一三是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么 为什么说我是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 二叶为什么会变成魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个和二叶同班的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春假有那个男孩的生日party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生只有二叶被邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝她不要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二叶非不听话一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐变成兄妹吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果气过头一不小心用了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 冒失烧掉了二叶的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个的影响…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 一三不要再说那种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二叶 等下啊 不要走那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都好有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光… 为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问我为什么 当然是因为我也变成魔法使了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才问你为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后会解释的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去参加入学式 回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果一直没有从月光那里听到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样时间不知不觉地流逝着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天 意想不到的事发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你撮下背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…月光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样的话 和武很难搭上话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也有自我反省
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止对武做了好多过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤后 自己的身体变得不听使唤 心情很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道不是武的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没有发泄的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点晚了 可我想好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直想着应该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武 你果然不会再原谅我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会原谅我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们和好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的春天 温暖蓬勃的气氛中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处处充满了希望与喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光 擦擦汗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 武
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六 白色情人节有收到七濑的回礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 和哥哥没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只属于两个人的秘密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我比收到谁的礼物比较开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安 维欧莉特老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七濑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一氏老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是和五十岛同学一起吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有伊田的妹妹和我的弟弟月光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 大家兄弟们融洽地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七濑同学 你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.30,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能和你的想法会非常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给弟弟当个好模范 为他指引方向可能会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课的时候不要来偷看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是去看看我可爱妹妹大显身手的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊田 不好好练习的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会被二叶超过的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤鱼看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 小武
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 什么事也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武 饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快向我偿罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要抢我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡桃 还有薄暮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回轮到我夺走你的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹫津 你怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌 我想动手的话早得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微想聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊天… 找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你让堂历史课
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然学校也有教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我的内容稍微有点不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在八世纪末
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法使被魔法使所统治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个统治阶层的魔法使是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫师气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫害的历史 在不同时代不断重演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 我再也不用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一生都不会再使用第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请放过我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要独占魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你们才是与众不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巫师气息的人就可以用魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世上 只有我们才被允许使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这等货色不配用魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法是高贵者才可以拥有的 神的恩赐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫师气息干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 与一部分人勾结 迫害弱小魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课上没教过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的直觉回避的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 话说你知道龙泉寺和马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们亡灵引路人的头领
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是和我一起学习魔法的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫师气息把力量强大而且能力特殊的和马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看作重要的战斗力 非常想他入伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你不加入巫师气息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被邀请了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对加入好 多难得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想加入啊 不过是考得上才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的能力的话 一定能当干部候选人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以加入精英行列的话要当仁不让啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们想要的只是当做战争道具的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的魔法是我自已的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用途径也要自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 巫师气息怎容这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和马同学 你不加入我们巫师气息的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会产生很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些关我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力如果只为个人使用会是相当危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你们来指导我 任听你们摆布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其当杀人的道具 还不如死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如死了吗 这真是太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是希望你活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母也是从心底希望你可以加入巫师气息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是儿子的话 实现父母的愿望是孝义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对他们做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是遵从规约的正规联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上放了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该先缔结契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文件已经备齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋日 在迟来晨曦的映射下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不考虑做出这种事后 你的父母会怎么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聆听镇魂的乐响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.40,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,657)}Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 和马的双亲被杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和马他啊 对充满对权利与金钱渴求的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傲慢的巫师气息忍无可忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且为了救济与自己有相似经历的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而创立了亡灵引路人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救济？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前听说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙泉寺和马杀害了大量的魔法使和普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是真的 他确实杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 那些家伙杀害的人数是和马的数百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是持续千年以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和马想为这一切画上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十世纪的末期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:16:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在东京 爆发了第一次魔法大战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全给我杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和马的一声令下 战争爆发了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲壮至极的战斗就要结束之时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月臣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快逃 阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七濑阳子 当时还是千木阳子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我们的魔法老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫师气息有十五位伟大的魔法使 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五位伟大的魔法使联合力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把世界一分为二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和马的左膀右臂 同时也是好朋友的藤川月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被千木阳子勾引 而背叛了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后为了保护阳子而牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是和马亲手杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和马是什么心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么… 为什么要告诉我这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想邀请你加入引路人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要加入引路人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那至少可以把那把剑还回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把剑是月臣的遗物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月臣那个笨蛋 从心底深爱着阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才存在薄暮这个证据
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把剑 绝不会把永远让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不要 那也不行 道理说不通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些事与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种人会第一个被当靶子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你已经是魔法使了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择吧 现在马上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引路人还是巫师气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法直接喊出加入巫师气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你还有救 我会等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你也会亲自找上我们门来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙的本质最终会在你的直觉回避下暴露无遗的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去确认下吧 找四条桃花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 学院长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 七濑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学院长在之前的大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以巫师气息的魔法使之身份参战了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的母亲 也是巫师气息的魔法使之事属实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 从哪听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那杀了龙泉寺和马双亲的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个男人鼓吹的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说见识过巫师气息的黑暗历史的冰山一角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可说引路人就是对的 这种判断也很武断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后要选择的还是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看能忍什么到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是目白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V 你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 这是眼泪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道已经醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉醒是阶段性的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在强行唤醒也只会再度沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:22:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的占卜中 和马大人的真正的觉醒之日不是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是X之日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我是魔女子·魔法子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是逃过腰斩一劫 迎来了第8集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止的道路非常凶险
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴满的行程表和不规律的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时甚至还会在下集预告的演说中突然昏倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的我遇到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个昴之绿园牌青汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.73,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了这个之后 体质大为改善
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:06.74,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1019,106)\fad(1200,250)}昴之绿园牌青汁的粉丝心声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(1019,265)\fad(1200,250)}纯属个人见解 毫无任何效果和疗效
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不苦 容易入口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还富含一天所需的营养成分 大力推荐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.99,0:24:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是下一集也要边吃饭边喝昴之绿园牌青汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:09.77,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\fs50\c&HFFA862&\blur2\pos(288,596)}迈向崩坏的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:08.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OOH YEAH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They bring me DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,all the world is stereotypical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They're Playing out rules
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but act another,look
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now you thought you had me by the upper-hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but I see through the face you've covered cynical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( FOUR )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,unleash the beast to fight inside at you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( THREE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To calm the fire that burns in front of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( TWO )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Without the fear and tears surrounding you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because your soul is what you were BORN TO BE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,たとえ今まで生きる(strategy) 夢失っても　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(It's time now)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:23:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ハンドルを切って 暴れる夢のまますっすっ進め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬のない人生に挑むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍もない感情を抱くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覚悟決めて行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自分自身をbreak away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全てを奪われる運命なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何を信じて生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ask yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the way there's nothing to live or die for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囲いも傷も恐れるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来さえも捨てるのはもんの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The choice is yours to make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is what I choose to live for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OOH YEAH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们令我无比失落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个世界都陈规蹈矩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在玩弄规则
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却演绎着另一个身份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在看起来 你自认为占了我的上风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我却看穿 那只是你用来掩盖愤世嫉俗的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( FOUR )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放荡不羁的兽性在你内心争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( THREE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰清冷静的火燃在你表面燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( TWO )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不再被恐惧和泪水所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的灵魂 与生俱有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你至今的人生战略使梦想尽失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(正是时机)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:23:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索性改变方向 沿着现在这狂荡的梦想继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要挑战没有严冬的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果怀有难以抑驭的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就做好觉悟勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把自己的身心解放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果注定是一切都被掠夺的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该以何信仰继续生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扪心自问
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有什么值得活着或是献身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果局限与伤害都令人恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就连未来也都丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你该作的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我选择的生存之道
